    {
      "index": 924,
      "id": "943e7109-0185-45c2-a7d4-48a555c44e68",
      "role": "user",
      "text": "in the MCP world I here a lot about skills you can download. You can easily download mcp servers. What do you know about \"skills\" Investigate this now",
