      "id": "f2ba3d57-1394-4e8f-8551-401ea8b7c4b8",
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "I’ll separate “skills” from “MCP servers,” because people often mix those terms. The failure mode is assuming every downloadable AI extension is an MCP server; several ecosystems use “skills” for different packaging models.",
