      "text": "I found the baseline content: current sources already encode Workspace/Task/Artifact, backend-first reads, transactional writes, and the previous MCP/Ollama plan. The update should not replace those; it should add the new tested facts: Promptbranch-native host, read-only MCP stdio, deterministic planner, broken Ollama planning, and a skills registry layer.",
